Name: Spaceship Trouble
About the game: Hey, pilot! Our spaceship get in trouble! We are in a dangerous place full of asteroids and pirates! Can you save your spaceship captain? Spaceship trouble is a 2D pixel arcade game, you have to reach highest score as you can! overcome waves of enemies as well as bosses on your own ship having problems, the game becomes more difficult with each wave, dodge meteorites so as not to become a simple piece of blizzardp Peculiarities: - Nice graphics - Nice soundtrack - Waves of enemies
